summary: This small mod adds extra foilage to Solitude to make it look prettier without impacting on performance.
descriptionHtml:
[center]
[size=4][u]What this mod is:
[/u][/size][size=3]This mod adds to the capital city of Skyrim with new shrubs, trees, plants and flowers to make it prettier to look at as you pass through on your adventure,[/size][size=3] whilst keeping it FPS friendly for lower end machines and (hopefully) keeping it lore-friendly.

P.S. I would love to see your screenshots!

[/size][size=4][u]Requirements:[/u]
[/size][size=3] [/size]
[size=3]-The latest Skyrim update (1.9.32.0.8)
 [/size]
[size=3] [/size]
[u][size=4]If you like this, why not try out my other mods:[/size][/u]

[size=3][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/45836/?]Whiterun Environment Project[/url][/size]
[size=3] [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51747/?]Village Environment Project[/url][/size]

[size=4][u]Compatibility:[/u]

[/size][size=3]This mod is incompatible with other mods that add to the interior of Solitude as well as any open city mod.[/size][/center]
author: Hallinskioi
